Interface SingleSuccessorUpdater

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface SingleSuccessorUpdater
extends LogicalModelUpdater
    General definition of updating methods returning a single successor. Such an updater can be determinist or stochastic, as denoted by the use of specialised interfaces.
